IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User mcardiff@hawk.iit.edu
PassCmd "gpg --quiet --for-your-eyes-only --no-tty --decrypt ~/.local/share/pass/mbsync/gmail.gpg"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/Mail/
Inbox ~/Mail/Inbox

Channel gmail
Far :gmail-remote:
Near :gmail-local:
Patterns * ![Gmail]* "[Gmail]/Sent Mail" "[Gmail]/Starred" "[Gmail]/All Mail" "[Gmail]/Trash"
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *